group cpgconditionemcareb23de03(source src, target tgt) {
  src.item first as item where linkId = 'EmCare.B23.DE03' then {
    item.answer first as a then {
      src.subject as sub -> tgt.subject = sub "23252e10";
      src.encounter as en -> tgt.encounter = en "553aae7e";
      src.item as item where linkId = 'timestamp' then {
        item.answer first as a then {
          a.value as val -> tgt.recordedDate = val "7a98a3e4";
        } "affc0db5";
      } "1ee842b8";
      src -> tgt.code = create('CodeableConcept') as cs then {
        src ->  tgt.code = create('CodeableConcept') as cs,  cs.coding = create('Coding') as ccs,  ccs.code = 'EmCare.B23.DE03',  ccs.system = 'https://fhir.dk.swisstph-mis.ch/matchbox/fhir/CodeSystem/emcare-custom-codes' "97f42802";
